                  <a id="main-content"></a>
                    <h1 class="page-header">Emo Public Library</h1>
                                                          <div class="region region-content">
    <section id="block-system-main" class="block block-system clearfix">

      
  <div id="node-39" class="node node-page clearfix" about="/emo-public-library" typeof="foaf:Document">

  
      <span property="dc:title" content="Emo Public Library" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="0" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
  
  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><h3 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to the Emo Public Library</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="img-responsive" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/sites/default/files/Library%20Head%20Banner%20.png" alt="Emo Public Library header" width="577" height="124" /></p>
<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" border="0" align="center"><tbody><tr valign="top"><td><img class="img-responsive" src="/sites/default/files/Screen%20Shot%202015-04-30%20at%209.37.50%20AM.png" alt="Emo waterfront" width="157" height="604" /></td>
<td>
<h2><span style="font-size: large;">                             </span></h2>
<h2><span style="font-size: large;">                                                        Spring Fever Days Book Sale!</span></h2>
<h3><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                                        April 21, 22, 23, 2016</span></h3>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                            Story Time - Tuesdays at 10:30am</span></strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                                                                                                   </span></strong></p>
<p>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            </p>
</td>
<td>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">The Emo Public Library is located on front street (just east of Queen Street) in downtown Emo.</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Address:</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Emo Public Library </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">Box 490 Emo, Ontario </span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">P0W 1E0</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Phone:</strong>  </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">(807) 482-2575</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>E-mail:</strong> <a title="emolib@bellnet.ca" href="mailto:emolib@bellnet.ca">emolib@bellnet.ca</a></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Librarian:</strong> Kathy Leek</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Winter Hours:</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Monday: 1-5pm</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Tuesday: 10am-7pm</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Wednesday: 1-5pm</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Thursday: 1-7pm</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Friday: 1-5pm</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Saturday 10am-2pm</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">CLOSED SUNDAY</span></p>
<p> </p>
</td>
</tr></tbody></table><p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">Be sure to check out all the following links, for library information. If you have any questions, comments, or suggestions please do not hesitate to contact <em>Kathy Leek</em> at the information below!</span></span> <br /><br /></p>
<table style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" border="0"><tbody><tr><td><a title="Download audiobooks and ebooks" href="http://downloadcentre.library.on.ca/98688E29-ACB4-456B-BE7D-D7B1A0E7EB63/10/50/en/Default.htm" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: medium;"><img class="img-responsive" src="/sites/default/files/img11.gif" alt="Download e-books" width="175" height="96" /></span></a></td>
<td><a title="Ancestry Library Edition" href="http://ancestrylibrary.proquest.com/aleweb/ale/do/login" target="_blank"><span style="font-size: medium;"><img class="img-responsive" src="/sites/default/files/img13.jpg" alt="Ancestry" width="132" height="83" /></span></a></td>
<td><span style="font-size: medium;"><a title="G1 Practice Test" href="http://epl.g1.ca/" target="_blank">C</a></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><a title="G1 Practice Test" href="http://epl.g1.ca/" target="_blank">lick for G1 Practice Test</a></span></td>
</tr></tbody></table><p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
