<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="https://olsn.ent.sirsidynix.net/client/en_US/emo/" href="https://olsn.ent.sirsidynix.net/client/en_US/emo/" target="_blank">Emo Library Catalogue</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="http://www.audiobookcloud.com/BooksList.aspx?categoryID=35&amp;subcategoryID=19" href="http://www.audiobookcloud.com/BooksList.aspx?categoryID=35&amp;subcategoryID=19" target="_blank">Tumble Talking Books</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/sites/default/files/banner.jpg" alt="banner" width="468" height="60" /></p>
<hr /><h3 style="text-align: center;"> Links</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><a title="http://infotrac.galegroup.com/itweb/ko_pl_emotpl?db=GVRL" href="http://infotrac.galegroup.com/itweb/ko_pl_emotpl?db=GVRL" target="_blank"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/sites/default/files/gale%20ref.jpg" alt="button" width="250" height="28" /></a> </p>
